rComments: Très bonne prof! Claire, intéressante, gentille... elle utilise des notes trouées, présente plusieurs films pour colorer ses cours. Bref, un prof et un cours bien plaisant! :)

In fact she is interesting to the point where you find that you have stopped taking notes and are just enjoying the class! Exams are fair, not too hard but not super easy either. Reccommended for psychologie!
